[Figures from Dr. Michael Sinsko, Senior Medical Entomologist at the
Indiana State Department of Health, give the following breakdown:
Lake County; 12 American Crows, 12 Blue Jays, 1 Common Grackle.
Porter County; 1 American Crow, 1 Blue Jay.
Marion County; 2 American Crows, 1 Sharp-shinned Hawk.
Floyd County; 4 Blue Jays, 3 American Crows.
Clark County; 1 Hawk.
Vanderburgh County; 1 Blue Jay.
